Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.84,0:00:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Woah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.93,0:00:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? You want a guitar too?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.26,0:00:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never played one, but...\Nyou think I could pull it off?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.10,0:00:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like Momoka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.48,0:00:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.73,0:00:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you've never played, right?\NJust focus on singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.57,0:00:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not even listening to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.87,0:00:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, performing for the first\Ntime tends to do that to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.12,0:00:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh, it's written all over her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.13,0:00:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Being able to pour out all of these repressed feelings...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.46,0:00:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Being able to scream them out at the top of my lungs...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.22,0:01:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the first time in my life I've ever felt like that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.02,0:01:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've always felt so conscious of people's judging glares,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.31,0:01:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that I was never able to express myself till now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.53,0:01:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.57,0:01:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.24,0:01:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.59,0:03:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}4: (SHOCKING) GRATITUDE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.30,0:03:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.89,0:03:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- What do you think?\N- Not bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.60,0:03:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it a listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.06,0:03:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wanna break.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.02,0:03:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've got no courage left!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.10,0:03:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Someone hurry and give me a reason to live.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.40,0:03:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm liking this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.19,0:03:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After all, there's many that--{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.11,0:03:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina, can you level it\Na bit more during the chorus?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.57,0:03:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Someone hurry and give me a reason to live.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.04,0:03:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.45,0:03:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it comes off as \Ntoo conventional otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.00,0:03:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, let's redo the drums.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Like, right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.59,0:03:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotta wake up early tomorrow, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.22,0:03:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Diamond Dust?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.93,0:03:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I saw her looking them up.\NYou think she's being self-conscious?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.14,0:03:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But like, aren't they actual pros by now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.14,0:03:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.14,0:03:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If she was really being conscious,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.19,0:03:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd she stick around\Nwith two amateurs like us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.65,0:03:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.78,0:04:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.20,0:04:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,NO WAY!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.87,0:04:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.95,0:04:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, gotta go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.87,0:04:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll... see you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.17,0:04:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Subaru-chan? You okay?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.58,0:04:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing serious ...right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.63,0:04:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Boyfriend, I'd guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.67,0:04:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,H-HUUH?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.01,0:04:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think she had one right now though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.59,0:04:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's some ex\Nor something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.09,0:04:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,W-what are you implying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.89,0:04:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you acting like it's {\i1}that{\i0} outrageous...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.02,0:04:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.31,0:04:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You think that's the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.89,0:04:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls in bands tend to be\Npretty popular with the boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.48,0:04:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,They're easy prey for the vultures.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.23,0:04:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...Prey?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.94,0:04:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be careful too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.61,0:04:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm calling her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.53,0:04:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,As if she'll reply. Again, I'm sure\Nshe'll tell us tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.03,0:04:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But hey, we've all got a right to\Ndate and work as we please, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.79,0:04:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you really feel though?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.04,0:05:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,About Diamond Dust, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.17,0:05:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Not much, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.47,0:05:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by "not much"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.13,0:05:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean that I'm not holding\Na grudge or anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.35,0:05:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,All I can do is just wish them good luck, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.27,0:05:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But then, why did you leave them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.19,0:05:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just drop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.11,0:05:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about what doesn't\Naffect you. Just keep on singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.32,0:05:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka-san. What was your band like?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.12,0:05:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I said drop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.12,0:05:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.26,0:05:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.43,0:05:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It all started as a school club.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.72,0:05:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But from the beginning, you could\Ntell we all had talent. And passion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.98,0:05:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We all felt like it had to be fate,\Nthat we had to chase this together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.65,0:06:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It felt like a miracle. I felt it in the goosebumps.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.19,0:06:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was right.　
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.32,0:06:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,As early as our first year's school festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.49,0:06:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,we had so many attendees they\Ncouldn't even fit in the auditorium.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.45,0:06:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Those times... they were the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.99,0:06:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We decided to drop out of school\Nand aim for going pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.62,0:06:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We came here, had our first indie CD, concert,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.21,0:06:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And then got signed with a major label!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.04,0:06:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...And then I gave it all up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.47,0:06:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.34,0:06:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen you smiling like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.02,0:06:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,S-sorry... I'm not sleeping I swear...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.41,0:06:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm gonna sleep,\NI should just do it on the bed...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.42,0:07:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Subaru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? WHAT?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.42,0:07:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Quitting the band. Sorry!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.71,0:07:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,HEY?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.59,0:07:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, if that's what she wants...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.09,0:07:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.43,0:07:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't the three of us swear we'd chase\Nthis together?! You'd give her up that easily?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.35,0:07:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mean it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.48,0:07:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If she values the band,\Nshe won't give us up for a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.31,0:07:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If we just force her back,\Nshe'll want to leave us all the more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.69,0:07:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You think...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.61,0:07:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me guess, never had a boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.28,0:07:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Momoka-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.04,0:07:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone home...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.58,0:07:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.21,0:07:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Being here again,\NI can't help but freeze up...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.88,0:07:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you're the band leader,\NI'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.55,0:07:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Leader? Since when?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.38,0:07:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, keep in mind Subaru-chan puts up\Nan annoying persona at school,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.05,0:07:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't hold it against her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.64,0:07:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.35,0:08:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Suba...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.56,0:08:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...who?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.57,0:08:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, grandmother, if you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,May I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.42,0:08:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- Suba--\N- Oh, are you lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.29,0:08:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandmother, give me a moment\Nso I can show them the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.47,0:08:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.43,0:08:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Why wouldn't we?!\NAfter that message you sent us...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.89,0:08:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll explain later, but\Nfor now just get out!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.68,0:08:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Not if you don't give us a good reason first!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.19,0:08:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I already said...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.65,0:08:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.65,0:08:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandmother!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.07,0:08:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They're... friends. Fellow actresses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.65,0:08:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Actresses?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.95,0:09:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\b1}Right?{\i0\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.71,0:09:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The glares can be quite overwhelming out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.17,0:09:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It {\i1}is{\i0} a busy place. Truly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.42,0:09:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Subaru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.09,0:09:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- Posture.\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.59,0:09:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't I told you enough times to mind your posture?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.01,0:09:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,One's habits manifest too evidently\Nwhen they are performing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.64,0:09:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We must always be composed in both heart and mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.77,0:09:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.48,0:09:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask you as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.81,0:09:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That you ensure she does not forget such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.65,0:09:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'll excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.28,0:09:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Subaru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,0:09:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.53,0:09:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that... Awa Tendo,\Nthe famous actress?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.79,0:09:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're {\i1}now{\i0} realizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.41,0:09:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How was I supposed to,\Nwhen no one told me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.04,0:09:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. She's my grandma alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.09,0:09:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she was visiting,\Ninsisting I show her around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.96,0:09:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? So you're from a showbiz family?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.51,0:09:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.43,0:10:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,My parents have normal jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.47,0:10:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But you don't want to be an actress, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.47,0:10:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not. But like I told you,\NI can't just spring that on her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.60,0:10:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why did you say\Nyou were quitting the band?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.27,0:10:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you could say I was panicking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.65,0:10:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't Sun Tzu say "To fool your enemies, you must first fool your allies"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.95,0:10:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're making no sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.28,0:10:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, goes to show how important\Nit is I keep fooling her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.66,0:10:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,She seems nice enough though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.62,0:10:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. At first glance. But she's from Kyoto,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.88,0:10:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you take her at face value, you'll come to regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.25,0:10:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.34,0:10:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- Posture!\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.55,0:10:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We should be taking our leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.34,0:10:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But I would like to get a look at\Nhow much your acting has improved first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.10,0:10:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...Sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.76,0:10:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Would the two of you care to join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.89,0:10:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...Sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.15,0:10:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,W-what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.44,0:10:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,T-t-the truth is... I have feelings? For you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.53,0:11:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.99,0:11:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,An... {\i1}etude{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.87,0:11:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed. Of a love scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.75,0:11:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You will confess your feelings for your friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.50,0:11:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,While her former lover, Subaru-chan,\Ntries to get her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.67,0:11:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...Sure.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.25,0:11:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}THE HELL IS AN ETUDE??{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.46,0:11:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What a wonderful idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.26,0:11:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Acting. Just improv it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.51,0:11:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let us hurry back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.51,0:11:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Improvise HOW??
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.97,0:11:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So, are you in?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.01,0:11:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}- No way!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.97,0:11:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}- Just deal with it
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.85,0:11:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}- There's literally no way \N- Come on!!\N- Fuck off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.97,0:11:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I must refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.94,0:11:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I think Nina-san\Nmust've misheard you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.07,0:11:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}NOW LISTEN HERE YOU LITTLE...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.69,0:11:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- DO IT. OR YOU WANT ME TO QUIT?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.49,0:11:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}- No means NO!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.28,0:11:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Please mind your phones, this is improv after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.99,0:11:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.54,0:11:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Then everyone, let us not be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.17,0:11:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.46,0:11:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-you must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.59,0:12:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I've realized I can't hide\Nmy feelings anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.47,0:12:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm also in love with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.77,0:12:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why did you leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.02,0:12:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.31,0:12:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I believed in you from\Nthe moment you accepted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.31,0:12:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I really believed we would never fall apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.77,0:12:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So how were you able to tell me\Nyou'd leave like it's nothing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.32,0:12:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.07,0:12:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.32,0:12:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Was everything you told me\Nback then a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.49,0:12:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I... meant it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.20,0:12:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what gives?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.10,0:12:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the worst! Using acting\Nas an excuse to lash out against me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.73,0:12:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see where's the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.48,0:12:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.69,0:12:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I want to quit the band.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.11,0:12:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, at school...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.94,0:13:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone only sees me as the granddaughter of Awa Tendo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.78,0:13:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's just...\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.24,0:13:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm worried I'll get caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.70,0:13:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the first time she's showed up all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.49,0:13:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not the type of person\Nto be spontaneous like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.63,0:13:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to be this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.92,0:13:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Girls Band Cry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.47,0:13:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're playing in a TV show?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.26,0:13:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch it! Don't speak into the mic!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.18,0:13:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I even do?\NMy grandma made the call.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.52,0:13:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so it shouldn't be long,\Nso I'll be free after a week or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.69,0:13:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But 'till then, no practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.40,0:13:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.23,0:13:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.44,0:13:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't you also skipped practice to study?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.99,0:13:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes it is! \N- No it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.20,0:13:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Chill out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.62,0:13:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But! Aren't you afraid\Nof losing Subaru-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.91,0:13:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It happens with bands.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.71,0:13:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.96,0:14:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with the tone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.84,0:14:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you don't seem to care.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.46,0:14:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who doesn't seem to care about us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.84,0:14:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I said I'll be back, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.93,0:14:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't you trust me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.76,0:14:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.06,0:14:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, everyone has something\Nthey're conscious about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.73,0:14:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you don't like it when\Npeople ask about your past, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.23,0:14:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.06,0:14:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We're wasting time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.61,0:14:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We only need to record the drums now,\Nso just go home, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.45,0:14:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm{\i0} the one who doesn't care?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.37,0:14:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.37,0:14:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You free tomorrow?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.37,0:14:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nope!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.13,0:14:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm lying!! I am!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you taking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.72,0:14:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? This is my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.01,0:14:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Make yourself at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.47,0:14:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}THE NEXT DAY
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.01,0:14:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.02,0:14:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You get used to it fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.02,0:14:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- Want some tea?\N- Y-yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.48,0:15:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Just sit wherever, I'll be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.15,0:15:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the best for gaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.32,0:15:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.24,0:15:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Check this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.12,0:15:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.00,0:15:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt I should be honest with you\Nbefore you snap at me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.00,0:15:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}STARRING: TENDO AWA
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.17,0:15:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}SUBARU
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.05,0:15:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I was named after this movie's title.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.30,0:15:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,My grandma insisted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.06,0:15:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So that actress is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.02,0:15:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. {\i1}Subaru{\i0} is the film that launched\Nher career when she was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.48,0:15:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Or so I'm told, since I wasn't born yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.32,0:15:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She said this name would bring me luck
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.40,0:15:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever I'd become an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.82,0:15:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But... you don't want to, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.99,0:15:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.12,0:16:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate having to live in the shadow\Nof my grandma. But more than that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.21,0:16:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate pretending to be who I'm not. It's uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.30,0:16:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.92,0:16:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,When I say I'll follow in her footsteps,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.43,0:16:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She smiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.01,0:16:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the only time she actually smiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.18,0:16:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Without putting a mask on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.95,0:16:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.99,0:16:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If it were you, what would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.58,0:16:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.79,0:16:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you get it now? You dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.91,0:16:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can't keep this up forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.71,0:16:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be better to be\Nhonest with her sooner than later?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.50,0:16:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You're probably right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.76,0:16:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I am right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.93,0:16:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hoping that if she saw I\Ncouldn't cut it at acting school,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.01,0:17:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,She'd just give up on it alltogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.35,0:17:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- See you later.\N- Mhm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.65,0:17:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- Don't worry. I won't leave.\N- Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.03,0:17:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,When we were playing the other day,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.57,0:17:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought... wow, I never realized\Nhow much I love this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.66,0:17:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to trust me, so say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.50,0:17:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.38,0:17:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.92,0:17:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I ' M  S O R R Y\N- N I N A.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.72,0:17:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're sorry, then\Ndon't get mad to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.10,0:17:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}SOME DAYS LATER...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.18,0:17:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting {\i1}Detective Grandma on the Case Part 6{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.65,0:17:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's welcome our main actress, Awa Tendo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.57,0:17:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,A pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.03,0:17:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm her granddaughter, Subaru.\NI'll be playing the cashier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.49,0:17:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.74,0:18:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She's practically drowning in makeup...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.12,0:18:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She's gotta go the extra mile, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.54,0:18:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Bands do so too, to look good on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.29,0:18:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- Huh? You also do makeup?\N- Sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.54,0:18:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop imagining things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.71,0:18:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Action!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.67,0:18:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You think she'll tell her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.47,0:18:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she said she would.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.26,0:18:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll probably have to quit acting school,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.01,0:18:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and stop living alone, but she\Nwants to continue with the band.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.39,0:18:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If it'll cause her that many problems,\Nthen maybe she should just keep at it for now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.98,0:18:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,True, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.31,0:18:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I think she's realized she\Ncan't run away from it forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.98,0:18:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.24,0:18:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's check the footage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.41,0:18:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everything good?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.66,0:18:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, my part for the day is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.50,0:18:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our first time acting together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.54,0:18:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be thrilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.79,0:18:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always dreamt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.84,0:18:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,To share the stage with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.63,0:19:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So you really want her\Nto become an actress?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.30,0:19:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.18,0:19:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Subaru shares her name with the\N movie that started my career.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.39,0:19:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, my daughter hates this business.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.61,0:19:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,She always resented me for the fact
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.48,0:19:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried pushing her into it despite\Noften not being at home for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.49,0:19:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can only imagine how I felt,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.82,0:19:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,when Subaru told me that she liked my acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.00,0:19:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She was the only one who smiled at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.54,0:19:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The only one who\Nliked me for my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.54,0:19:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So when she said she wanted\Nto try it, I felt so grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.17,0:19:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.55,0:19:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's check.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.01,0:19:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, let me see it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.43,0:19:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandmother!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.93,0:19:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.61,0:19:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ehm, I would like to talk for a moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.78,0:19:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk? About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.28,0:20:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It could wait until later, but you might\Nnot make the Shinkansen back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.66,0:20:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Good point. I do not have much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.91,0:20:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.83,0:20:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.67,0:20:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.83,0:20:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.21,0:20:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.05,0:20:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.13,0:20:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.68,0:20:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I want...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.60,0:20:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Subaru-chan! Emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.39,0:20:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot something! We need to hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.48,0:20:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta hurry! Let's go! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.36,0:20:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wha- Ouch, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.07,0:20:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't push me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.86,0:20:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.62,0:20:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You say one thing, then you do another?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.95,0:20:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My bad!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.25,0:20:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.21,0:20:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What gives? You weren't lying when\Nyou said I should just tell her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.17,0:20:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- Well, yeah.\N- Then why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.05,0:21:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,After I finally got the courage...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.34,0:21:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just... everyone has\Nsomething they're conscious about.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.68,0:21:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Things aren't always that simple,\Nso you have to be careful about this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.43,0:21:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- Right?\N- Who do you think you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.31,0:21:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch ouch ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.02,0:21:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What makes you think you can\Npreach us after all that's happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.86,0:21:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.78,0:21:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But you still need to tell her someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.45,0:21:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,When?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.86,0:21:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,When you become sure about\Nwhat you want to do in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.20,0:21:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this girl, I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.91,0:21:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.29,0:21:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh, screw this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.96,0:21:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw this, screw this, screw this!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.59,0:21:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You told me not to quit, so I made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.88,0:21:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet I get stuck between a\Nbipolar self-righteous freak,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.18,0:21:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And an emotionless know-it-all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.26,0:21:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll choose my life for myself! Leave me alone!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.56,0:21:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Subaru-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.44,0:22:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So? How's my acting?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.61,0:22:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaah, I needed that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.82,0:22:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah well, I figured I'd have to come\Nto terms with it on my own someday,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.95,0:22:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So until then, I'll be here to kick your asses into shape!
